ADDITIONS

FOR ALLOWANCE FOR DOUBTFUL ACCOUNTS AND ALLOWANCE FOR INVENTORY LOSSES ARE CHARGED TO EXPENSE AND COST ACCOUNTS, RESPECTIVELY, WHILE REVENUE BASED

PROVISIONS ARE CHARGED TO REVENUE ACCOUNTS.

